text: Oosterscheldekering is a dam and storm surge barrier between the islands Schouwen-Duiveland and Noord-Beveland. It is the largest of the 13 ambitious Delta Works made to protect the Netherlands from flooding from the North Sea. ==Other websites== * DeltaWorks.org - DeltaWorks.Org about Oosterscheldekering. Includes text, photos, video and virtual tour.
